<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Some people prefer to transform column names in the accessor methods of Zend_Db_Table_Row, for example to provide inflection syntax.</p>

<p>Please create a common protected method in Zend_Db_Table_Row_Abstract to transform the column name from the form it is specified in the application, to the form required by the database.</p>

<p>Call this method in the __get(), __set(), and __isset() methods.</p>

